---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Terms & Conditions | HEIC to JPG Converter — browserpixels"
	description="Terms and conditions for the free, private HEIC to JPG converter. Using the client-side HEIC to JPG converter means you accept these terms."
	canonicalPath="/terms"
>
	<main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-5 py-14 transition-colors duration-300 sm:py-20">
		<header class="mb-10">
			<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-neutral-900 transition-colors duration-300 dark:text-white sm:text-4xl">
				Terms and Conditions
			</h1>
			<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-neutral-500 transition-colors duration-300 dark:text-slate-400 sm:text-base">
				Last updated: July 12, 2026
			</p>
		</header>

		<div class="space-y-10 text-sm leading-relaxed text-neutral-600 transition-colors duration-300 dark:text-slate-300 sm:text-base">
			<section>
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 transition-colors duration-300 dark:text-white">
					1. Agreement to terms
				</h2>
				<p class="mt-3">
					These Terms and Conditions govern your use of The Private Image Converter (the "Service"). By accessing or using the Service, you agree to be bound by these terms. If you do not agree with any part of them, please do not use the Service.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 transition-colors duration-300 dark:text-white">
					2. What the Service does
				</h2>
				<p class="mt-3">
					The Service is a browser-based tool that converts HEIC and WebP image files to JPG format. All processing takes place locally on your device; your files are not uploaded to any server.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 transition-colors duration-300 dark:text-white">
					3. Use of the Service
				</h2>
				<p class="mt-3">
					You may use the Service only for lawful purposes and in a way that does not infringe the rights of others. You agree not to misuse the Service, attempt to disrupt it, or reverse-engineer it beyond what is permitted by applicable law.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 transition-colors duration-300 dark:text-white">
					4. Intellectual property
				</h2>
				<p class="mt-3">
					All images you convert remain your property — we never receive them. The Service's name, design, and code are owned by us and are provided for your personal and commercial use, subject to these terms. You may not redistribute the Service itself or claim it as your own.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 transition-colors duration-300 dark:text-white">
					5. Disclaimer of warranties
				</h2>
				<div class="mt-3 rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-5 text-neutral-800 transition-colors duration-300 dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 sm:p-6">
					<p>
						The Service is provided <strong class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white">"as is"</strong> and <strong class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white">"as available"</strong>, without warranties of any kind — whether express or implied — including but not limited to implied warranties of merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, or non-infringement. We do not warrant that the Service will be error-free, uninterrupted, or that conversions will always be accurate or complete.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 transition-colors duration-300 dark:text-white">
					6. Limitation of liability
				</h2>
				<p class="mt-3">
					While we strive for accuracy, we are not responsible for any data loss or corrupted files during conversion. You are solely responsible for keeping backups of your original images before using any conversion tool, including this one. To the fullest extent permitted by law, we shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from your use of the Service.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 transition-colors duration-300 dark:text-white">
					7. Third-party links and advertising
				</h2>
				<p class="mt-3">
					The Service may display advertising provided by third parties such as Google AdSense, and may contain links to external websites. We are not responsible for the content, policies, or practices of those third parties or external sites.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 transition-colors duration-300 dark:text-white">
					8. Changes to the Service and terms
				</h2>
				<p class="mt-3">
					We may modify or discontinue the Service at any time, and may update these terms accordingly. Continued use after changes are posted constitutes acceptance of the revised terms.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 transition-colors duration-300 dark:text-white">
					9. Governing law
				</h2>
				<p class="mt-3">
					These terms are governed by applicable law in the jurisdiction in which the Service is operated. Any disputes will be resolved in the courts of that jurisdiction.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 transition-colors duration-300 dark:text-white">
					10. Contact us
				</h2>
				<p class="mt-3">
					If you have questions about these Terms and Conditions, contact us at
					<a class="font-medium text-emerald-700 underline decoration-emerald-300 underline-offset-2 transition-colors duration-300 hover:decoration-emerald-500 dark:text-emerald-400 dark:decoration-emerald-700" href="mailto:hello@browserpixels.com">hello@browserpixels.com</a>.
				</p>
			</section>

			<footer class="pt-6">
				<a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm font-medium text-emerald-700 transition-colors duration-300 hover:text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400 dark:hover:text-emerald-300">
					← Back to the converter
				</a>
			</footer>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>
